<br>
*prolly among the most balanced class pre 60 (cept they cant taunt reds pre 60, which is embarrasing at times when you MT'ing a red mob)<br>
<br>
*most HP hands down (not that much more then other classes but will remain ahead of others none the less) <br>
<br>
*wars solo for crap pre and post 60 so if you want to solo lots war not for you (unless you have a cleric/druid/shaman on 2nd pc)<br>
<br>
*drinal in general doesnt seem to be lacking in war's too much, so getting into a guild maybe difficult (wizzies really have advantage here, can never hace enough wizzies with sol and insane melee mitigation) pallies are less "desireable" in guild settings then wars generally speaking. <br>
<br>
