<br>
*other then monkies,  war's (least first two on MT list)prolly die more then other classes on big raids, which can be a pain in the ass to regain that xp back, wizzies and pallies generally dont die as much as war's on raids. <br>
<br>
*war aa's really are lacking, only true good AA's war get is in the arch section and area taunt, the rest of the stuff is of limited use (ambidex is ok tho). pallies, wizzies come out on top here as well, <3 5points for 103k horse <br>
